{"name":"Roller","description":"A jQuery plugin for simple content carousels. ","version":"3.2.3","demo":"http:\/\/formstone.it\/components\/Roller\/demo\/index.html","repository":"https:\/\/github.com\/Formstone\/Roller","documentation":{"options":[{"name":"autoAdvance","type":"boolean","default":"false","description":"Flag to auto advance items"},{"name":"autoTime","type":"int","default":"8000","description":"Auto advance time"},{"name":"autoWidth","type":"boolean","default":"false","description":"Flag to fit items to viewport width"},{"name":"controls","type":"boolean","default":"true","description":"Flag to draw controls"},{"name":"customClass","type":"string","default":"''","description":"Class applied to instance"},{"name":"infinite","type":"boolean","default":"false","description":"Flag for looping items"},{"name":"labels.next","type":"string","default":"'Next'","description":"Control text"},{"name":"labels.previous","type":"string","default":"'Previous'","description":"Control text"},{"name":"maxWidth","type":"string","default":"'Infinity'","description":"Width at which to auto-disable plugin"},{"name":"minWidth","type":"string","default":"'0'","description":"Width at which to auto-disable plugin"},{"name":"paged","type":"boolean","default":"false","description":"Flag for paged items"},{"name":"pagination","type":"boolean","default":"true","description":"Flag to draw pagination"},{"name":"single","type":"boolean","default":"false","description":"Flag for single items"},{"name":"touchPaged","type":"boolean","default":"true","description":"Flag for paged touch interaction"},{"name":"useMargin","type":"boolean","default":"false","description":"Use margins instead of css transitions (legacy browser support)"}],"events":[{"name":"update.roller","description":"Canister position updated"}],"methods":[{"name":"defaults","description":"Sets default plugin options","params":[{"name":"opts","type":"object","default":"{}","description":"Options object"}],"example":"$.roller(\"defaults\", opts);"},{"name":"destroy","description":"Removes instance of plugin","example":"$(\".target\").roller(\"destroy\");"},{"name":"disable","description":"Disables instance of plugin","example":"$(\".target\").roller(\"disable\");"},{"name":"enable","description":"Enables instance of plugin","example":"$(\".target\").roller(\"enable\");"},{"name":"jump","description":"Jump instance of plugin to specific page","example":"$(\".target\").roller(\"jump\", 1);"},{"name":"resize","description":"Resizes each instance","example":"$(\".target\").roller(\"resize\");"},{"name":"reset","description":"Resets instance after item change","example":"$(\".target\").roller(\"reset\");"},{"name":"_init","description":"Initializes plugin","params":[{"name":"opts","type":"object","description":"Initialization options"}],"private":true},{"name":"_build","description":"Builds each instance","params":[{"name":"$roller","type":"jQuery object","description":"Target jQuery object"},{"name":"opts","type":"object","default":"{}","description":"Options object"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onImageLoad","description":"Handles child image load","params":[{"name":"e","type":"object","description":"Event data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onTouchStart","description":"Handles touchstart event","params":[{"name":"e","type":"object","description":"Event data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onTouchMove","description":"Handles touchmove event","params":[{"name":"e","type":"object","description":"Event data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onTouchEnd","description":"Handles touchend event","params":[{"name":"e","type":"object","description":"Event data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_autoAdvance","description":"Handles auto advancement","params":[{"name":"data","type":"object","description":"Instance data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onAdvance","description":"Handles item advancement","params":[{"name":"e","type":"object","description":"Event data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onSelect","description":"Handles item select","params":[{"name":"e","type":"object","description":"Event data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_position","description":"Handles updating instance position","params":[{"name":"data","type":"object","description":"Instance data"},{"name":"index","type":"int","description":"Item index"}],"private":true},{"name":"_updateControls","description":"Handles updating instance controls","params":[{"name":"data","type":"object","description":"Instance data"}],"private":true},{"name":"_onRespond","description":"Handles media query match change","private":true},{"name":"_calculateIndex","description":"Determines new index based on current position","params":[{"name":"data","type":"object","description":"Instance data"}],"return":{"type":"int","description":"New item index"},"private":true},{"name":"_prefix","description":"Builds vendor-prefixed styles","params":[{"name":"property","type":"string","description":"Property to prefix"},{"name":"value","type":"string","description":"Property value"}],"return":{"type":"string","description":"Vendor-prefixed styles"},"private":true},{"name":"_startTimer","description":"Starts an internal timer","params":[{"name":"timer","type":"int","description":"Timer ID"},{"name":"time","type":"int","description":"Time until execution"},{"name":"callback","type":"int","description":"Function to execute"},{"name":"interval","type":"boolean","description":"Flag for recurring interval"}],"private":true},{"name":"_clearTimer","description":"Clears an internal timer","params":[{"name":"timer","type":"int","description":"Timer ID"}],"private":true},{"name":"_getTransform3DSupport","description":"Determines if transforms are support","return":{"type":"boolean","description":"True if transforms supported"},"private":true}]},"files":{"js":["jquery.fs.roller.js"],"css":["jquery.fs.roller.css"]},"extra":"","demo_resources":"<!--[DEMO:START-RESOURCES]-->\n\n\t\t<style>\n\t\t\t.demo .rolled .roller-item { background: #ccc; color: #fff; font-size: 100px; height: 294px; line-height: 290px; margin: 0 10px 0 0; text-align: center; width: 294px; }\n\t\t\t.demo .rolled .roller-viewport { overflow: hidden; }\n\n\t\t\t.demo .rolled.single .roller-controls,\n\t\t\t.demo .rolled.single .roller-pagination { clear: both; }\n\n\t\t\t.demo .rolled .roller-page.active { color: #000; }\n\t\t<\/style>\n\n\t\t<script>\n\t\t\t$(document).ready(function() {\n\t\t\t\t$(\".demo .rolled\").roller();\n\n\t\t\t\t$(window).on(\"snap.roller\", function() {\n\t\t\t\t\t$(\".demo .rolled\").roller(\"reset\");\n\t\t\t\t});\n\n\t\t\t\t$(\".demo_tabbed\").on(\"update.tabber\", function() {\n\t\t\t\t\t$(\".demo .rolled\").roller(\"reset\");\n\t\t\t\t});\n\n\t\t\t\t$(window).one(\"pronto.load\", function() {\n\t\t\t\t\t$(\".demo .rolled\").roller(\"destroy\");\n\t\t\t\t\t$(window).off(\"snap.roller\");\n\t\t\t\t\t$(\".demo_tabbed\").off(\"update.tabber\");\n\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t});\n\t\t<\/script>\n\n\t\t","demo_content":"<!--[DEMO:START-CONTENT]-->\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- BASIC -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Basic<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>The basic Roller comes almost completely un-styled, giving you the flexibility to integrate it into your project how you see fit. At a minimum you will need to set a height and width for the <code>roller-item<\/code> elements so dimensions can be calculated:<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">$(\".target\").roller();<\/code><\/pre>\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-css\">.roller-item { height: 300px; width: 300px; }<\/code><\/pre>\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;div class=\"target\"&gt;\n\t&lt;div class=\"roller-item\"&gt;\n\t\t\/\/ Content\n\t&lt;\/div&gt;\n\t&lt;div class=\"roller-item\"&gt;\n\t\t\/\/ Content\n\t&lt;\/div&gt;\n\t&lt;div class=\"roller-item\"&gt;\n\t\t\/\/ Content\n\t&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;\/div&gt;<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h5>Demo<\/h5>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rolled\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-viewport\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-canister\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- PAGED -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Paged<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>Bt default, Roller will calculate page sizes by determining how many <code>roller-item<\/code> elements will fit in the <code>roller-viewport<\/code> at once. You can opt to have Roller stop at every <code>roller-item<\/code> element by setting the <code>paged<\/code> option at initialization:<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">$(\".target\").roller({\n\tpaged: true\n});<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h5>Demo<\/h5>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rolled\" data-roller-options='{\"paged\":\"true\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- AUTO WIDTH -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Auto Width<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>Roller will base all calculations on the item's widths, allowing items with varying widths to exists in the same instance. You can also set Roller to automatically resize all of it's items to the viewport width.<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">$(\".target\").roller({\n\tautoWidth: true\n});<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h5>Demo<\/h5>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rolled\" data-roller-options='{\"autoWidth\":\"true\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- SINGLE -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Single<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>To display a single item at a time:<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">$(\".target\").roller({\n\tsingle: true\n});<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h5>Demo<\/h5>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rolled\" data-roller-options='{\"single\":\"true\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- INFINITE -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Infinite<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>Roller can also infinitely loop instead of having hard start and stop positions:<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">$(\".target\").roller({\n\tinfinite: true\n});<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h5>Demo<\/h5>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rolled\" data-roller-options='{\"infinite\":\"true\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- BREAKPOINT -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Breakpoint<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>By default, each Roller instance will enable itself on all screen sizes. You can specify a different width by setting either the <code>maxWidth<\/code> or <code>minWidth<\/code> option on initialization.<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"example\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">$(\".target\").roller({\n\tminWidth: \"740px\"\n});<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h5>Demo<\/h5>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rolled\" data-roller-options='{\"minWidth\":\"740px\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"roller-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t<!-- IE -->\n\t\t\t\t<h2>IE Support<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p>When supporting IE you will need to include a <a href=\"https:\/\/gist.github.com\/benplum\/8045366\" target=\"_blank\">HTML5 enabler<\/a> and matchMedia polyfill (<a href=\"https:\/\/gist.github.com\/benplum\/8045336\" target=\"_blank\">IE 8<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/gist.github.com\/benplum\/8045327\" target=\"_blank\">IE 9<\/a>). <\/p>\n\n\t\t\t\t"}